headline: Does Strong da Vinci Growth and 2026 Guidance Change The Bull Case For Intuitive Surgical (ISRG)?
summary: In recent days, Intuitive Surgical reported a strong past quarter, with revenue rising 19% year over year on higher procedure volumes and more da Vinci system placements, alongside improved non‑GAAP profitability. The company also highlighted robust adoption of its da Vinci 5 and SP platforms and guided for 13–15% global da Vinci procedure growth in 2026, underlining how procedure expansion is reinforcing its recurring instruments and services business. headline: Intuitive Surgical Revenue Growth And AI Push Shape Robotic Surgery Outlook
summary: Intuitive Surgical (NasdaqGS:ISRG) reported 19% year-over-year revenue growth in fiscal 2025 Q4. Growth was driven by higher procedure volumes and increased placements of da Vinci robotic systems. The company is expanding the use of artificial intelligence across its platforms. Recent AI efforts include work on robotic bronchoscopies and lung biopsies.
